post_text:
Remember why you started with us...Stick to the plan we have set in place for you to achieve your goal of a high school diploma. You have all the tools you need right at your fingertips!

1. Log in daily to reach at least 34% progress. (7% per day if you are working 5 days a week)
2. Communicate with your teacher for attendance and support.
3. Your teachers are still available to help you in your classes.

#onlinehighschool #wearestillinsession #diploma #workhard #alternativehighschoolsinmichigan #focusongraduation

Nothing makes us happier than seeing our students with big smiles on their faces!

Students at Success VLC aren't full of school-related stress because our program allows them to focus their attention on one class at a time. Not having to balance all of their subjects at once helps them to succeed in each class.

If you're looking for an alternative to your traditional high school, please come into one of our learning centers. We would love to chat with you about your high school needs!
